17e05c9513de6bf5869f561bf30ec4d9","tid":2298443,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:23:39.000Z","msg":"陳雲：是日精彩對答。<br />\nA.L. : 以前真愛聯嘅反諷式遊行攪笑又安全兼到肉，不過港豬太蠢唔明。如果舊年百萬人遊行係真愛聯方式，港共一早縮啦，唉⋯<br />\n陳雲：是囉。如果我做，一定是用文革方式，將香港十大富豪公仔有名有姓綁住送中，嚇死資本家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10158691208442225/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10158691208442225%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=180ba820\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10158691208442225/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"151a1ac81ed5aa6eea06844e6d835e4b345d0bb5","tid":2298443,"uid":3776,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:26:46.000Z","msg":"之前美領遊行搶頭位喎又搶住交請願信"},{"pid":"93995c1357a0126a752d97a2731dc6f7f6f747c4","tid":2298443,"uid":205099,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"迷雲黨不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8ad39ddf93ea2168e13ef3299d5adcbed57bfb","tid":2298443,"uid":284147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"中國是地球的中國。這是愛球者的中國定位。 我愛地球甚於中共愛地球。<br />\n分別就在這裡！"},{"pid":"a9eec7fd0646509304d51d7757b11450e3b58bb1","tid":2298443,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"貨真價實的港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bd62a4ee0089c95c04c6ccec594d489b232621","tid":2298443,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"佢講野好似五涼液廣告"},{"pid":"5022052dbcedc317825ee5467f07fbd2c7d647e6","tid":2298443,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"香港人：香港是香港的香港"},{"pid":"c5f27677e4b61d24dc539de7001259ee8fda19df","tid":2298443,"uid":45376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r